  Call for Papers: The Fintech RevolutionThis year, our highlight theme will be The Fintech Revolution. Thanks to advanced technologies, the pace of revolution in FinTech area has never been faster. Fintech has dramatically changed the way customers and financial institutions make transactions in our daily lives.Many tech advances have been already in use in Fintech companies, helping banks better detect fraud transaction, providing customized services, developing new commerce interfaces and etc. Although there is still progress to be made in todays technologies, Fintech is expected to play a big role in the future global business.2020 IRCET invites submission of abstracts/full papers relevant to Engineering and Technology, especially in the fields bellowedTopics (Special Session): 1. Application Programming Interface Technologies2. Artificial Intelligence in Fintech3. Biometrics Technology4. BlockchainIoTMachine Learning and Fintech5. Data & Natural Language Processing Engineering6. Information Security7. Robotic Process AutomationSubmitImportant DatesSubmission Deadline: September 10, 2019Notification of Acceptance: September 30, 2019Payment Deadline: November 08, 2019  

